      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">During a review session with interns, you decide to test their knowledge on vaccine strains with a matching exercise. Match the following vaccines with their respective strains:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cerebellum-web-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/public/images/2024/03/22/picture6.jpg\" style=\"height:273px; width:700px\" /></span></span></span></p>",
