      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">On your first day in the pediatric department, while acquainting yourself with the surroundings dedicated to the care of children, you encounter a distinctive logo featuring a rainbow and a baby. This emblem represents a particular immunization program. You ponder which vaccines are encompassed by this program. Based on your knowledge, which of the following vaccines is NOT typically included in the program symbolized by the rainbow and baby logo?</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cerebellum-web-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/public/images/2024/03/22/picture5.jpg\" style=\"height:169px; width:300px\" /></span></span></span></p>",
